701358f.title: Bronx: Jerome Avenue - 205th Street (East)
701358f.text:
Jerome Ave., north fromm East 205ih Street (right) to Van Cortlandt Ave.
East, showing the elevated structure of the II.R.T. Woodlawn subway line
and houses on the east side of the Avenue.
December 3, 1936.
Works Progress Administration.
Federal Art Project photo.
